Package model

Class Ingredient

java.lang.Object
model.Ingredient
public class Ingredient extends Object
Represents an ingredient used in products, including its name, unique identifier, and any allergens associated with it. This class is designed to be compatible with CSV serialization and deserialization using OpenCSV.
Version:
0.1
Author:
DaniAndries
